{"type":"message","id":"0450d33e","parentId":"e7bda56d","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:09:33.464Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说采购价格要严格控制在5块以内（人民币）。这意味着：\n- 采购价 ≤ ¥5（人民币）\n- 但这个价格要能达到70%毛利率的话，TikTok售价需要更高\n\n让我算一下：\n- 采购价 ¥5 ≈ $0.69\n- 物流费 = 售价 × 15%\n- 平台佣金 = 售价 × 30%\n\n要达到70%毛利率：\n(售价 - 0.69 - 售价×0.15 - 售价×0.30) / 售价 = 0.70\n售价 - 0.69 - 0.45×售价 = 0.70×售价\n0.55×售价 - 0.69 = 0.70×售价\n-0.69 = 0.15×售价\n售价 = $4.6\n\n所以如果采购价是¥5，要达到70%毛利率，TikTok售价必须≥$4.6\n\n但用户的意思是：采购价5块以内，这样才能有足够利润。\n\n我需要更新SOP，把采购价上限写进去。\n","thinkingSignature":"c3ab7bd9fe2749b2ebf698fbfbe9e583c3424fef9d2e688b6ed7a67b074f9af0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，采购价严格≤¥5。这个逻辑是对的，采购价控制在5块以内才能保证毛利空间。\n\n反过来算一下：\n- 采购价¥5 ≈ $0.69\n- 物流费15% + 平台佣金30% = 45%\n- 要70%毛利率 → 留给采购+物流+佣金的只有30%\n\n**验证：**\n```\n毛利率70% = 1 - 0.45(物流+佣金) - 0.69/售价\n0.70 = 0.55 - 0.69/售价\n0.69/售价 = 0.15\n售价 = $4.6\n```\n\n所以**采购价≤¥5的前提下，TikTok售价只要做到$4.6以上就能有70%毛利**。发夹品类$6-$15完全没问题。\n\n我把采购价上限写进SOP：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d2561699a97c4ec4a76bdfde","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## 采购价格管控（核心红线）\n\n**1688采购价必须≤¥5元人民币**（含混批/MOQ≤20件的价格）\n\n这不是建议，是铁律。超过¥5的品直接放弃，无论它销量多好。\n\n原因：\n- ¥5采购价 + 物流15% + 平台30% = 售价的45%固定成本\n- 要70%毛利，剩余55%空间 - 45%固定成本 = 10%留给采购余量\n- 即：采购价每降低¥1，毛利率直接提升约2-3个百分点\n\n---\n\n## 核心原则：毛利率必须≥70%","oldText":"## 核心原则：毛利率必须≥70%"}],"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57546,"output":625,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58171,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780643351769,"responseId":"0671a918e7ff9d8ea71cd52c9f3f672b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3f69de5","parentId":"0450d33e","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:09:33.677Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d2561699a97c4ec4a76bdfde","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n   7 > 输出终点：飞书多维表格（去掉妙手ERP）\n   8 \n   9 ---\n  10 \n+ 11 ## 采购价格管控（核心红线）\n+ 12 \n+ 13 **1688采购价必须≤¥5元人民币**（含混批/MOQ≤20件的价格）\n+ 14 \n+ 15 这不是建议，是铁律。超过¥5的品直接放弃，无论它销量多好。\n+ 16 \n+ 17 原因：\n+ 18 - ¥5采购价 + 物流15% + 平台30% = 售价的45%固定成本\n+ 19 - 要70%毛利，剩余55%空间 - 45%固定成本 = 10%留给采购余量\n+ 20 - 即：采购价每降低¥1，毛利率直接提升约2-3个百分点\n+ 21 \n+ 22 ---\n+ 23 \n  11 ## 核心原则：毛利率必须≥70%\n  12 \n  13 **所有费用放里面（含平台扣点30%），如果毛利率没有70-80%，必赔无疑。**\n  14 \n     ...","patch":"--- /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md\n+++ /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md\n@@ -7,8 +7,21 @@\n > 输出终点：飞书多维表格（去掉妙手ERP）\n \n ---\n \n+## 采购价格管控（核心红线）\n+\n+**1688采购价必须≤¥5元人民币**（含混批/MOQ≤20件的价格）\n+\n+这不是建议，是铁律。超过¥5的品直接放弃，无论它销量多好。\n+\n+原因：\n+- ¥5采购价 + 物流15% + 平台30% = 售价的45%固定成本\n+- 要70%毛利，剩余55%空间 - 45%固定成本 = 10%留给采购余量\n+- 即：采购价每降低¥1，毛利率直接提升约2-3个百分点\n+\n+---\n+\n ## 核心原则：毛利率必须≥70%\n \n **所有费用放里面（含平台扣点30%），如果毛利率没有70-80%，必赔无疑。**\n \n","firstChangedLine":11},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780643373676}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1bf9e45","parentId":"e3f69de5","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:09:42.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，已经更新了。现在我需要告诉用户更新完成，并且总结一下核心改动点。\n","thinkingSignature":"56c81765f5b48e58bd9e1d1988fd9aedaa17b2bbd18a8b8ea1239892a0a65d64"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已更新。核心改动总结：\n\n| 问题 | 旧标准 | 新标准 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 毛利率门槛 | ≥40% | **≥70%** |\n| 采购价上限 | 未限定 | **≤¥5** |\n| 发夹价格带 | $1.5-$8 | **$6-$15** |\n\n**现在跑选品的时候**，毛利率计算会是这样：\n```\n毛利率 = (售价 - $0.69 - 售价×0.45) / 售价\n```\n只要选售价$6以上的发夹，毛利率轻松破70%。\n\n下次跑数据的时候我会严格按这个标准筛，不够70%毛利的一律不写进去。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3653,"output":164,"cacheRead":54561,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780643373689,"responseId":"0671a92e9bd0233f19a5644dfb688b7b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c660d1d","parentId":"f1bf9e45","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:22:05.375Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"我的意思是我们既要灵活也要准确，才能找到黑马产品，你选品的数据 都是40000越南盾一下的， 也就是别人的销售价格， 怎么赚钱。","timestamp":1780644124809}}
{"type":"message","id":"f81f5f05","parentId":"1c660d1d","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:22:34.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is making a very valid point. They're saying:\n\n1. Their product selection data shows items under 40,000 VND (Vietnamese Dong)\n2. 40,000 VND ≈ $1.6 USD (at exchange rate of ~25,000 VND/USD)\n3. If the TikTok selling price is only ~$1.6, how can they make money after all the costs?\n\nThey're right - if the selling price is too low (under $2), even with 70%+ margin, the absolute profit is tiny. \n\nLet me think about this:\n- 40,000 VND ≈ $1.6 USD\n- Platform fee 30% = $0.48\n- Logistics 15% = $0.24\n- Remaining for product cost + profit = $0.88\n- If product cost is $0.69 (¥5), then profit before other costs = $0.19\n- After other costs (storage, damage, returns), essentially break-even or loss\n\nSo the user's point is:\n1. The selection data shows selling prices around 40,000 VND (~$1.6) - that's the TikTok selling price\n2. That's way too low to make any real profit\n3. They need to find products that are SELLING at higher price points (not just the cheap ones)\n\nThe user is saying: \"Your selection data shows items all under 40,000 VND, which is the selling price. How can you make money from that?\"\n\nThis makes complete sense. The problem isn't just the margin percentage - the problem is the absolute price point. Even with 80% margin on a $1.6 product, you only make $1.28 gross profit, and after all other costs you're barely breaking even or losing money.\n\nThe user wants products that sell at higher price points - meaning they should be looking at:\n- Hair clips that sell for 100,000-200,000+ VND ($4-$8)\n","thinkingSignature":"4f8ed48e37caaf3dd0472259499c7324ba2ac017c3c0bedd2887baa66c9449b7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to:om_x100b6d13df714084c35e949c169e2c2]]\n\n说得太对了！\n\n40,000 越南盾 ≈ $1.6 美元——这个价位哪怕毛利率100%，利润空间也极薄。平台扣30%就去了$0.48，物流15%去了$0.24，剩下$0.88要cover采购+仓储+退货+人工，根本不够。\n\n**问题核心：** 我们选到的都是低价跑量的品，不是黑马爆款。黑马发夹应该要有**100,000-200,000+越南盾（$4-$10+）**的售价，才能真正赚钱。\n\n让我查一下最近的选品数据，确认一下是不是真的抓的全是低价品：\n\n我来查一下最近一次采集的数据，看看价格分布：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ee236fd10c046ff8345b700","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd","page_size":20,"table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27959,"output":668,"cacheRead":30425,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780644125440,"responseId":"0671ac1e32e7f85fb8a3ac63575fe3b6"}}
