{"type":"message","id":"d85a07ba","parentId":"057d1a52","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:53:27.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the actual MCP tools available from Sorftime. I can try calling the sorftime-mcp to list its tools. Let me check if there's a way to see what tools are available. I'll also look at the task agent or task list to see what MCP tools are registered.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is asking: \"Can't you scan the data types and formats provided by Sorftime MCP?\" - they want me to understand what Sorftime actually returns and use it to filter properly.\n\nI should check what Sorftime actually returns for each tool, particularly the `tiktok_product_trend` tool, to see if we can filter by price at the Sorftime level.\n\nLet me try calling the tiktok_product_trend tool to see what it returns, and understand what filters we can apply.\n","thinkingSignature":"5ed42503ff0caefaab12d8358e5d1ba384f14abd97253d05becc088b12e5a4c4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我直接调 Sorftime 的工具看看返回什么字段，然后找出能筛高价品的方式：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_70c44e08cc0c42c782b249e2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' | mcporter call sorftime-mcp --json 2>/dev/null || echo \"mcporter call failed\"\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/list\",\"params\":{},\"id\":1}\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3569,"output":261,"cacheRead":60904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646000465,"responseId":"0671b37068293f75b601e78db9c665c0"}}
