{"type":"message","id":"3eaeba9c","parentId":"1d284020","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:54:44.295Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bb52a210b8314c3582d1c9e0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: mcporter\ndescription: \"List, configure, authenticate, call, and inspect MCP servers/tools with mcporter over HTTP or stdio.\"\nhomepage: http://mcporter.dev\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"📦\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"mcporter\",\n              \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install mcporter (node)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# mcporter\n\nUse `mcporter` to work with MCP servers directly.\n\nQuick start\n\n- `mcporter list`\n- `mcporter list <server> --schema`\n- `mcporter call <server.tool> key=value`\n\nCall tools\n\n- Selector: `mcporter call linear.list_issues team=ENG limit:5`\n- Function syntax: `mcporter call \"linear.create_issue(title: \\\"Bug\\\")\"`\n- Full URL: `mcporter call https://api.example.com/mcp.fetch url:https://example.com`\n- Stdio: `mcporter call --stdio \"bun run ./server.ts\" scrape url=https://example.com`\n- JSON payload: `mcporter call <server.tool> --args '{\"limit\":5}'`\n\nAuth + config\n\n- OAuth: `mcporter auth <server | url> [--reset]`\n- Config: `mcporter config list|get|add|remove|import|login|logout`\n\nDaemon\n\n- `mcporter daemon start|status|stop|restart`\n\nCodegen\n\n- CLI: `mcporter generate-cli --server <name>` or `--command <url>`\n- Inspect: `mcporter inspect-cli <path> [--json]`\n- TS: `mcporter emit-ts <server> --mode client|types`\n\nNotes\n\n- Config default: `./config/mcporter.json` (override with `--config`).\n- Prefer `--output json` for machine-readable results.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646084294}}
{"type":"message","id":"b042df33","parentId":"3eaeba9c","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:54:48.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand how to use mcporter. Let me try to list the Sorftime MCP tools to see what schemas and data types they return.\n","thinkingSignature":"2e3581537978bc38dcf1b01b00cbbd4fba6906a654f98d2da97413f927a9d547"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7c69e9478cd476aabbe70f1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter list sorftime-mcp --schema 2>&1 | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4060,"output":81,"cacheRead":63563,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67704,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646084318,"responseId":"0671b3c5a8d525aefb5945f85c333058"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c4478d9","parentId":"b042df33","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:54:51.425Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7c69e9478cd476aabbe70f1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"sorftime-mcp\n\n  /**\n   * 查询我的Shopee平台关键词词库的词\n   *\n   * @param dict? 选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\n   * @param site? Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\n   */\n  function shopee_get_favorite_keyword(dict?: string, page?: number, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品详情\n   *\n   * @param productId 产品Id\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_product_detail(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 搜索亚马逊电商平台上的潜力产品\n   *\n   * @param searchName? 可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\n   * @param price_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param price_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param delivery_type? 可选参数，如果指定，筛选产品的发货方式\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function potential_product(searchName?: string, price_min?: number, price_max?: number, month_sales_volume_min?: number, month_sales_volume_max?: number);\n  // optional (3): delivery_type, page, amzSite\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"price_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"price_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"delivery_type\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定，筛选产品的发货方式\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Both\",\n              \"FBM\",\n              \"FBA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Both\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品趋势，同时返回`销量`，`价格`，`星级`，`评论数量`，`新增带货视频数`，`新增带货达人数`多个维度\n   *\n   * @param productId 产品Id\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_product_trend(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 移动我的Shopee平台关键词词库中收藏的关键词到指定收藏夹，如果收藏夹不存在会新建\n   *\n   * @param keyword 需要移动的词\n   * @param toDict 移动到的收藏夹名称\n   * @param fromDict? 选填，如果指定，将移动指定收藏夹下的词\n   * @param site? Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\n   */\n  function shopee_change_favorite_keyword(keyword: string, toDict: string, fromDict?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要移动的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"toDict\": {\n            \"description\": \"移动到的收藏夹名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2555,"aggregated":"sorftime-mcp\n\n  /**\n   * 查询我的Shopee平台关键词词库的词\n   *\n   * @param dict? 选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\n   * @param site? Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\n   */\n  function shopee_get_favorite_keyword(dict?: string, page?: number, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品详情\n   *\n   * @param productId 产品Id\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_product_detail(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 搜索亚马逊电商平台上的潜力产品\n   *\n   * @param searchName? 可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\n   * @param price_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param price_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param delivery_type? 可选参数，如果指定，筛选产品的发货方式\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function potential_product(searchName?: string, price_min?: number, price_max?: number, month_sales_volume_min?: number, month_sales_volume_max?: number);\n  // optional (3): delivery_type, page, amzSite\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"price_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"price_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"delivery_type\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定，筛选产品的发货方式\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Both\",\n              \"FBM\",\n              \"FBA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Both\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品趋势，同时返回`销量`，`价格`，`星级`，`评论数量`，`新增带货视频数`，`新增带货达人数`多个维度\n   *\n   * @param productId 产品Id\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   */\n  function tiktok_product_trend(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 移动我的Shopee平台关键词词库中收藏的关键词到指定收藏夹，如果收藏夹不存在会新建\n   *\n   * @param keyword 需要移动的词\n   * @param toDict 移动到的收藏夹名称\n   * @param fromDict? 选填，如果指定，将移动指定收藏夹下的词\n   * @param site? Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\n   */\n  function shopee_change_favorite_keyword(keyword: string, toDict: string, fromDict?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要移动的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"toDict\": {\n            \"description\": \"移动到的收藏夹名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646091423}}
{"type":"message","id":"867349a1","parentId":"1c4478d9","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:54:57.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the Sorftime tools now. The key tools are:\n\n1. `tiktok_product_trend(productId, site)` - takes productId and site, returns trend data including 销量, 价格, 星级, 评论数量, 新增带货视频数, 新增带货达人数\n2. `tiktok_product_detail(productId, site)` - takes productId and site, returns product details\n3. `potential_product` - Amazon product search with price_min, price_max filters\n\nThe problem is that `tiktok_product_trend` takes a `productId` - it doesn't search by category. It means we need to first get a list of product IDs somehow (maybe from Shopee or Amazon), then pass them to `tiktok_product_trend` to get trends.\n\n\nSo the workflow seems to be: either search Amazon for products with `potential_product`, then pull those product IDs into TikTok trend analysis, or use Shopee keyword searches to find related products and cross-reference them with TikTok data.\n\nLet me check what other tools are available beyond what I've seen so far.\n","thinkingSignature":"9719d2664f8895aedf31b81abae2bdedf53b6920967803184e093a9447bb5694"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e0893f9b5d6346d1aec8b2c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter list sorftime-mcp --schema 2>&1 | grep -A 30 \"function \" | head -400"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5350,"output":285,"cacheRead":64050,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69685,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646091443,"responseId":"0671b3cb861fbaba068eb19358de90c6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca17ada0","parentId":"867349a1","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:00.944Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e0893f9b5d6346d1aec8b2c5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function shopee_get_favorite_keyword(dict?: string, page?: number, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，查询指定收藏夹下的词；如需查询全部词，指定传值`all`\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回100条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        }\n--\n  function tiktok_product_detail(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 搜索亚马逊电商平台上的潜力产品\n   *\n--\n  function potential_product(searchName?: string, price_min?: number, price_max?: number, month_sales_volume_min?: number, month_sales_volume_max?: number);\n  // optional (3): delivery_type, page, amzSite\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"price_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"price_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"number\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_min\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"month_sales_volume_max\": {\n            \"description\": \"可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": -9999\n          },\n          \"delivery_type\": {\n--\n  function tiktok_product_trend(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 移动我的Shopee平台关键词词库中收藏的关键词到指定收藏夹，如果收藏夹不存在会新建\n   *\n--\n  function shopee_change_favorite_keyword(keyword: string, toDict: string, fromDict?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要移动的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"toDict\": {\n            \"description\": \"移动到的收藏夹名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"fromDict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，将移动指定收藏夹下的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n--\n  function shopee_product_request(productId: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要查询的产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n--\n  function shopee_favorite_keyword(keyword: string, dict?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要收藏的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，将添加词到指定收藏夹\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n--\n  function product_variations(asin: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"asin\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品ASIN，仅支持单ASIN查询\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n--\n  function walmart_keyword_search_results(keyword: string, page?: number);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"keyword\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 支持产品五大维度历史趋势：星级、评论数、价格、累计销量、近30日销量\n   *\n   * @param productId 需要查询的产品Id\n   * @param queryStart? 选填，查询趋势的时间段的开始时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认近1年。查询时间超过1年时，每次调用消耗变为10。\n   * @param queryEnd? 选填，查询趋势的时间段的结束时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认为当前时间。\n   * @param site? Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\n   */\n  function shopee_product_trend(productId: string, queryStart?: string, queryEnd?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要查询的产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"queryStart\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，查询趋势的时间段的开始时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认近1年。查询时间超过1年时，每次调用消耗变为10。\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": null\n          },\n          \"queryEnd\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，查询趋势的时间段的结束时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认为当前时间。\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": null\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n--\n  function shopee_del_favorite_keyword(keyword: string, dict?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"SG\" | \"TH\" | \"MY\" | \"TW\" | \"PH\" | \"BR\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要删除的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"dict\": {\n            \"description\": \"选填，如果指定，将删除指定收藏夹下的词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"default\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"Shopee站点，支持：201:VN，202:ID，203:SG，204:TH，205:MY，206:TW，207:PH，208:BR\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"UnKonw\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"SG\",\n              \"TH\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"TW\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"BR\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"UnKonw\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n--\n  function tiktok_product_video_author(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询产品在Tiktok平台上的相似产品，可用于分析此类产品的销售情况\n   *\n--\n  function tiktok_similar_product(searchName: string, page?: number, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的产品名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\","}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646100942}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7758d82","parentId":"ca17ada0","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:11.856Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much clearer picture. The key tools are:\n\n1. **`tiktok_similar_product(searchName, page, site)`** - Search similar products on TikTok by name. This is a search/listing tool that takes a product name keyword and returns products.\n\n2. **`tiktok_product_trend(productId, site)`** - Get trend data for a specific product (销量, 价格, 星级, 评论数, 新增带货视频数, 新增带货达人数)\n\n3. **`tiktok_product_detail(productId, site)`** - Get product details for a specific product\n\n4. **`shopee_product_request(productId, site)`** - Get Shopee product details\n\n\n5. **`shopee_product_trend(productId, site)`** - Get Shopee product trends\n\n6. **`ali1688_similar_product(productName)`** - Find 1688 similar products (need to see this one)\n\nThe challenge is that I'm working backwards from results I already have - I need to figure out which TikTok products meet my criteria (price ≥ $2 for hair clips, growth trends) and then trace back to their Shopee equivalents and 1688 sources for supplier verification.\n\nLet me check what parameters `ali1688_similar_product` accepts to understand the full flow.\n","thinkingSignature":"4270b75a524ec84e79c4d4aec2c13c9ee4e57079baaf322a6255510ee629ef74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_43f8c0e06b344c52a55a24c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter list sorftime-mcp --schema 2>&1 | grep -A 50 \"ali1688\\|similar_product_feature\\|category_name_search\\|category_report\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7077,"output":335,"cacheRead":65674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646100965,"responseId":"0671b3d5ea9aa28b489df2da6c2a3770"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d4d25bc","parentId":"b7758d82","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:15.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_43f8c0e06b344c52a55a24c5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function category_name_search(categoryName: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"categoryName\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要查询的类目市场名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"categoryName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 按指定大品类（如汽车用品，家居用品）搜索亚马逊电商平台上相关的细分类目（品类）市场，按销量倒序排列返回数据。\n   *\n   * @param topNode 在指定大品类下搜索（如汽车用品，家居用品），先通过CategoryTree获取，数据类型：string\n   * @param month_sales_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param month_sales_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param ratings_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选星级大于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param ratings_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选星级小于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param ratings_count_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选评论数量大于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param ratings_count_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选评论数量小于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param price_min? 可选参数，如果指定如果指定表示筛选平均销售价（当地货币，如US为美元，FR为欧元）大于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param price_max? 可选参数，如果指定如果指定表示筛选平均销售价（当地货币，如US为美元，FR为欧元）小于等于此值的细分类目市场\n   * @param seasonal_popular_product? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选在指定月份为热销旺季的细分类目\n   * @param top3Product_sales_share_min? 可选参数，用0-1表示百分比数(如10% 为\n   *                                     0.1)。如果指定表示筛选Top3产品在Top100产品的销量占比（销量垄断系数）大于等于此值的细分类目市场\n--\n  function walmart_category_report_by_node_id(nodeId: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"细分类目nodeId，查询这个指定细分类目数据\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台**指定类目**的**指定历史时间段**销量Top100产品数据报告\n   *\n   * @param startDate 查看历史数据，指定起始时间（格式：yyyy-MM-dd）\n   * @param endDate 查看历史数据，当指定起始时间后（startDate）后用于指定查询截止时间，支持最长40天数据组合\n   * @param nodeId 细分类目nodeid，查询这个指定细分类目数据，数据类型：string\n   * @param amzSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function category_report_from_history(startDate: string, endDate: string, nodeId: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"startDate\": {\n            \"description\": \"查看历史数据，指定起始时间（格式：yyyy-MM-dd）\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"endDate\": {\n            \"description\": \"查看历史数据，当指定起始时间后（startDate）后用于指定查询截止时间，支持最长40天数据组合\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"细分类目nodeid，查询这个指定细分类目数据，数据类型：string\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"startDate\",\n          \"endDate\",\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台细分类目市场趋势数据，基于类目Top100产品统计\n   *\n   * @param nodeId 查询类目的nodeid，数据类型：string\n   * @param trendIndex? 所查询的趋势类型\n--\n  function ali1688_similar_product(searchName: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的产品名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"searchName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询亚马逊电商平台上热搜关键词的延伸词关键词，可用于卖家查询相关关键词、发现长尾词或挖掘个性化需求\n   *\n   * @param keyword 查询的关键词\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function keyword_extends(keyword: string, page?: number, keywordSupportSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"keyword\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的关键词\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"keywordSupportSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n--\n  function similar_product_feature(productName: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productName\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询的类目名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"productName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 搜索亚马逊电商平台上的**实时**产品数据，默认按月销量倒序排列\n   *\n   * @param seasonal_popular_product? 可选参数，如果指定，将筛选在指定月份为热销旺季的产品\n   * @param brand? 可选参数，如果指定，将筛选此品牌的产品\n   * @param seller_name? 可选参数，如果指定，将筛选此卖家的产品\n   * @param searchName? 可选参数，如果指定，将按此名称搜索相关产品\n   * @param property_name? 可选参数，如果指定，将筛选产品标题或属性中包含指定property的产品\n   * @param price_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param price_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选销售价小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param month_sales_volume_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选月销量小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param ratings_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选星级大于等于此值的产品\n   * @param ratings_max? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选星级小于等于此值的产品\n   * @param ratings_count_min? 可选参数，如果指定表示筛选评论数量大于等于此值的产品\n--\n  function category_report(nodeId: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"细分类目nodeid，查询这个指定细分类目数据，数据类型：string\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"amzSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"GB\",\n              \"DE\",\n              \"FR\",\n              \"IN\",\n              \"CA\",\n              \"JP\",\n              \"ES\",\n              \"IT\",\n              \"MX\",\n              \"AE\",\n              \"AU\",\n              \"BR\",\n              \"SA\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 查询产品历史趋势数据，将返回按月统计的销量趋势、按月统计的累计销量趋势、按月统计的销售额趋势、按月统计的平均价格趋势、按月统计的评论数量趋势、按月统计的星级趋势。\n   *\n   * @param productId 需要查询的产品Id\n   * @param queryStart? 选填，查询趋势的时间段的开始时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认近1年。查询时间超过1年时，每次调用消耗变为10。\n   * @param queryEnd? 选填，查询趋势的时间段的结束时间，格式:yyyy-MM-dd。默认为当前时间。\n   * @param site? Temu站点，支持：701:US, 705:EU\n   */\n  function temu_product_trend(productId: string, queryStart?: string, queryEnd?: string, site?: \"UnKonw\" | \"US\" | \"EU\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"productId\": {\n            \"description\": \"需要查询的产品Id\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n--\n  function tiktok_category_name_search(searchName: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"searchName\": {\n            \"description\": \"搜索的产品名称\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"searchName\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 用于查询该类目市场历史趋势\n   *\n   * @param nodeId? 需要查找的NodeId\n   * @param trendIndex? 所需要查询的历史趋势类型\n   *                    0：月销量趋势\n   *                    1：月销额趋势\n   *                    2：平均价格趋势\n   *                    3：平均评价数趋势\n   *                    4：平均星级趋势\n   *                    5：卖家数量趋势\n   *                    6：平均变体数趋势\n   *                    7：品牌数量趋势\n   *                    8：旗舰店铺数趋势\n   *                    9：旗舰店铺占比趋势\n   *                    10：旗舰店铺月销量趋势\n   *                    11：旗舰店铺月销量占比趋势\n   *                    12：优选店铺数趋势\n   *                    13：优选店铺占比趋势\n   *                    14：优选店铺月销量趋势\n   *                    15：优选店铺月销量占比趋势\n   *                    16：普通店铺数趋势\n   *                    17：普通店铺占比趋势\n--\n  function tiktok_category_report(nodeId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"nodeId\": {\n            \"description\": \"类目市场nodeid，可通过TiktokCategoryNameSearch获得\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"site\": {\n            \"description\": \"TikTok站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"Unknow\",\n              \"US\",\n              \"MY\",\n              \"PH\",\n              \"VN\",\n              \"ID\",\n              \"GB\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"Unknow\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"nodeId\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * 获取亚马逊电商平台产品的竞品在各核心关键词下的曝光位置，这里只会使用自然曝光计算（排除了广告曝光），以此可以分析此产品获取流量的能力（例如：在搜索量大的核心词下都有排名靠前的曝光，就说明获取流量能力强；反之则有待加强）\n   *\n   * @param asin 产品ASIN\n   * @param page? 查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\n   * @param keywordSupportSite? 亚马逊站点\n   */\n  function competitor_product_keywords(asin: string, page?: number, keywordSupportSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"asin\": {\n            \"description\": \"产品ASIN\",\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"page\": {\n            \"description\": \"查询结果的页码索引，默认为第1页。每页返回20条数据\",\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"default\": 1\n          },\n          \"keywordSupportSite\": {\n            \"description\": \"亚马逊站点\",\n            \"type\": \"string\","}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646115163}}
{"type":"message","id":"b10e4291","parentId":"4d4d25bc","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:26.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture of the Sorftime MCP tools. Let me look at the most relevant ones for our workflow:\n\n**Key TikTok tools:**\n1. `tiktok_category_name_search(searchName, site)` - Search for TikTok category node IDs by product name. This is how we find the category nodeId for hair clips, headbands, etc.\n2. `tiktok_category_report(nodeId, site)` - Get category market data (Top100 products by sales for a specific category nodeId)\n3. `tiktok_similar_product(searchName, page, site)` - Search similar products on TikTok by name keyword. **This returns real products with their prices!**\n\n\n4. `tiktok_product_trend(productId, site)` - Get trend data for a specific product\n\nThe critical insight is that `tiktok_category_report` and `tiktok_similar_product` are our main entry points for discovering products, but the current SOP incorrectly describes `tiktok_product_trend` as a batch interface when it actually only accepts a single productId.\n\nLooking at the real tools available, I need to use `tiktok_category_name_search` to find nodeIds for specific Vietnamese product categories like hair clips, headbands, hair ties, and hair sticks, then pass those nodeIds to `tiktok_category_report` to get the actual product data.\n\nThe problem is that `tiktok_category_report` doesn't support price filtering—all products in the category come back regardless of cost. But `tiktok_similar_product` does accept price parameters, so I could search for premium hair clip products and use that to filter by price range, then validate the results against other criteria.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the real issue might be upstream: the category node IDs we've been using from earlier sessions may be pointing to low-price categories like basic hair ties. If I search for \"hair clips\" or \"claw clips\" using `tiktok_category_name_search`, I should get nodeIds for higher-priced items that actually match what the user is looking for.\n","thinkingSignature":"3c8d5d738b1d27a50b8820708f10128e5fd1405fafdbf178c716df8cd21b2151"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_91202959271d4bfa9352a62f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 搜索 TikTok 越南站的发夹类目，看看有哪些类目节点\ncd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"hair clips\" site=VN --output json 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7743,"output":500,"cacheRead":68812,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646115188,"responseId":"0671b3e3aa6db6ce78d9889d1c3190da"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b410f3f","parentId":"b10e4291","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:32.523Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_91202959271d4bfa9352a62f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Hair Clips & Hair Pins\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"908552\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Phụ kiện tóc cho bé\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"962696\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Headbands\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"605271\"\n  }\n]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5871,"aggregated":"[\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Hair Clips & Hair Pins\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"908552\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Phụ kiện tóc cho bé\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"962696\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"类目名称\": \"Headbands\",\n    \"nodeid\": \"605271\"\n  }\n]","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646132522}}
{"type":"message","id":"51d8d568","parentId":"6b410f3f","timestamp":"2026-06-05T07:55:37.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the nodeIds. Let me try searching for more categories like hair claws, headwraps, hair sticks, etc. Also let me try searching for \"hair accessories\" and other terms.\n","thinkingSignature":"13d345b293cf7ad6f99ce912e9260f22eea4cfe445cbd9be394f46190c619e03"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e4880a7a8b66494781bd16ac","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 搜索更多发饰类目\ncd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"hair claw\" site=VN --output json 2>&1 && echo \"---\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"headband\" site=VN --output json 2>&1 && echo \"---\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"hair accessory\" site=VN --output json 2>&1 && echo \"---\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"bobby pin\" site=VN --output json 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4531,"output":220,"cacheRead":72622,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646132545,"responseId":"0671b3f507587a3017552f340ac0a73d"}}
