{"type":"message","id":"df6680ad","parentId":"7190ec86","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:06:57.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! TH doesn't work but GB and US do. Let me check GB Hair Clips since it's a high-income market with likely higher prices.\n","thinkingSignature":"b64b611b495ce402a238a22734eb71d70f759e6216a08542aeafc4cc97f3dcef"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\nTH不行，但GB英国和US美国可以！让我查英美市场的发夹价格带：\n\n**这才是真正的高利润市场！**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_682a57025cad400f850ced46","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\necho \"=== GB 英国 Hair Clips ===\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=908552 site=GB --output json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json, re\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint(f'类目: {d[\\\"类目名称\\\"]} | 均价: {d[\\\"平均价格\\\"]} | 中位数: {d[\\\"中位数价格\\\"]} | 增长: {d[\\\"月销量环比\\\"]}%')\ntop50 = d.get('Top50产品', [])\ndef get_price(p):\n    try: return float(re.sub(r'[^\\d.]', '', str(p.get('价格','0'))))\n    except: return 0\nsorted_prods = sorted(top50, key=get_price, reverse=True)\nfor i, p in enumerate(sorted_prods[:15], 1):\n    price = p.get('价格','N/A')\n    title = p.get('标题','N/A')[:55]\n    sales = p.get('月销量', 0)\n    stars = p.get('星级','N/A')\n    growth = p.get('周销量环比', 0)\n    print(f'{i:2d}. {price:>8s} | 月销{sales:>6d} | ⭐{stars} | 增长{growth:>7.1f}% | {title}')\n\"\n\necho \"\" && echo \"=== US 美国 Hair Clips ===\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=908552 site=US --output json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json, re\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint(f'类目: {d[\\\"类目名称\\\"]} | 均价: {d[\\\"平均价格\\\"]} | 中位数: {d[\\\"中位数价格\\\"]} | 增长: {d[\\\"月销量环比\\\"]}%')\ntop50 = d.get('Top50产品', [])\ndef get_price(p):\n    try: return float(re.sub(r'[^\\d.]', '', str(p.get('价格','0'))))\n    except: return 0\nsorted_prods = sorted(top50, key=get_price, reverse=True)\nfor i, p in enumerate(sorted_prods[:15], 1):\n    price = p.get('