{"type":"message","id":"79f51ef0","parentId":"73896f12","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:08:25.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they should enable/start the Malaysia (MY) site for their product selection strategy. Based on what I found, MY has significantly better price points than VN/TH:\n- MY Headbands avg $7.52, +13% growth\n- MY Hair Accessories avg $7.52, +13% growth\n\nAnd I found a black swan product: $69 MYR headband with +171% weekly growth.\n\nLet me give a clear recommendation.\n","thinkingSignature":"f62b62669f430e4a553e79403322b64feff9f6da6359ca33b420ee60c8780144"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n要！马来 MY 完全值得开。\n\n我扫完所有站点的结论：\n\n| 站点 | 发饰品类均价 | 月增长 | 推荐度 |\n|------|------------|--------|--------|\n| **MY 马来** | **$7.52** | **+13%** ✅ | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| PH 菲律宾 | $57 (但儿童配件为主) | +30% | ⭐⭐ |\n| VN 越南 | $1.11-$1.46 | -2%到+60% | ⭐⭐ |\n| GB 英国 | $4.92 | -4% | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| US 美国 | $10.72 | -44% | 竞争太激烈 |\n\n---\n\n**MY 站开荒的理由：**\n\n1. **价格是越南的5倍** —— 均价 $7.52 VS 越南 $1.1\n2. **增长稳定 +13%** —— Headbands 类目月月涨，不是昙花一现\n3. **已发现黑马** —— $69 MYR 高端棉发带，周增长 +171%\n4. **市场成熟度适中** —— 比越南贵但比英美竞争小\n\n---\n\n**下一步建议：**\n\n立刻把 **MY Hair Accessories (nodeId=905864) + MY Headbands (nodeId=605271)** 加入每日扫描，筛选价格 **≥$5 MYR** 的品，再过 1688 利润验证。\n\n要我先把 SOP 更新成「VN+MY 双站点策略」，然后马上跑一轮 MY 的高价产品出来吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18901,"output":428,"cacheRead":77668,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780646894926,"responseId":"0671b6ef1f9423b2b981f4ab4d865432"}}
