{"type":"message","id":"4d9b60fb","parentId":"d7bbb946","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:09:23.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_78f5973878f74a799acf8f4d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 3. 单选 (type=3)\n\n**Property 结构**:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"options\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"进行中\",   // 必填，选项名称\n      \"color\": 0         // 可选，颜色编号 (0-54)\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"已完成\",\n      \"color\": 10\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**颜色编号 (color)**:\n- 范围: 0-54\n- 0: 红色\n- 10: 绿色\n- 20: 蓝色\n- ... (详见飞书官方文档)\n\n**示例**:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": 3,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":169,"aggregated":"### 3. 单选 (type=3)\n\n**Property 结构**:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"options\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"进行中\",   // 必填，选项名称\n      \"color\": 0         // 可选，颜色编号 (0-54)\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"已完成\",\n      \"color\": 10\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**颜色编号 (color)**:\n- 范围: 0-54\n- 0: 红色\n- 10: 绿色\n- 20: 蓝色\n- ... (详见飞书官方文档)\n\n**示例**:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": 3,","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646963054}}
