{"type":"message","id":"7f4d538b","parentId":"a72257ab","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much clearer picture. The key tools are:\n\n1. **`tiktok_similar_product(searchName, page, site)`** - Search similar products on TikTok by name. This is a search/listing tool that takes a product name keyword and returns products.\n\n2. **`tiktok_product_trend(productId, site)`** - Get trend data for a specific product (销量, 价格, 星级, 评论数, 新增带货视频数, 新增带货达人数)\n\n3. **`tiktok_product_detail(productId, site)`** - Get product details for a specific product\n\n4. **`shopee_product_request(productId, site)`** - Get Shopee product details\n\n\n5. **`shopee_product_trend(productId, site)`** - Get Shopee product trends\n\n6. **`ali1688_similar_product(productName)`** - Find 1688 similar products (need to see this one)\n\nThe challenge is that I'm working backwards from results I already have - I need to figure out which TikTok products meet my criteria (price ≥ $2 for hair clips, growth trends) and then trace back to their Shopee equivalents and 1688 sources for supplier verification.\n\nLet me check what parameters `ali1688_similar_product` accepts to understand the full flow.\n","thinkingSignature":"4270b75a524ec84e79c4d4aec2c13c9ee4e57079baaf322a6255510ee629ef74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_43f8c0e06b344c52a55a24c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter list sorftime-mcp --schema 2>&1 | grep -A 50 \"ali1688\\|similar_product_feature\\|category_name_search\\|category_report\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7077,"output":335,"cacheRead":65674,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646100965,"responseId":"0671b3d5ea9aa28b489df2da6c2a3770"}}
