{"type":"message","id":"21843b79","parentId":"8303723f","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture of the Sorftime MCP tools. Let me look at the most relevant ones for our workflow:\n\n**Key TikTok tools:**\n1. `tiktok_category_name_search(searchName, site)` - Search for TikTok category node IDs by product name. This is how we find the category nodeId for hair clips, headbands, etc.\n2. `tiktok_category_report(nodeId, site)` - Get category market data (Top100 products by sales for a specific category nodeId)\n3. `tiktok_similar_product(searchName, page, site)` - Search similar products on TikTok by name keyword. **This returns real products with their prices!**\n\n\n4. `tiktok_product_trend(productId, site)` - Get trend data for a specific product\n\nThe critical insight is that `tiktok_category_report` and `tiktok_similar_product` are our main entry points for discovering products, but the current SOP incorrectly describes `tiktok_product_trend` as a batch interface when it actually only accepts a single productId.\n\nLooking at the real tools available, I need to use `tiktok_category_name_search` to find nodeIds for specific Vietnamese product categories like hair clips, headbands, hair ties, and hair sticks, then pass those nodeIds to `tiktok_category_report` to get the actual product data.\n\nThe problem is that `tiktok_category_report` doesn't support price filtering—all products in the category come back regardless of cost. But `tiktok_similar_product` does accept price parameters, so I could search for premium hair clip products and use that to filter by price range, then validate the results against other criteria.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the real issue might be upstream: the category node IDs we've been using from earlier sessions may be pointing to low-price categories like basic hair ties. If I search for \"hair clips\" or \"claw clips\" using `tiktok_category_name_search`, I should get nodeIds for higher-priced items that actually match what the user is looking for.\n","thinkingSignature":"3c8d5d738b1d27a50b8820708f10128e5fd1405fafdbf178c716df8cd21b2151"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_91202959271d4bfa9352a62f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 搜索 TikTok 越南站的发夹类目，看看有哪些类目节点\ncd /home/halei/workspace-tts && mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"hair clips\" site=VN --output json 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7743,"output":500,"cacheRead":68812,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646115188,"responseId":"0671b3e3aa6db6ce78d9889d1c3190da"}}
