{"type":"message","id":"c1ab939d","parentId":"4a845b0f","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.445Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_af35cfa0ecba40c29ac24d36","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 2132 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3372,"aggregated":"=== MY站 Hair Clips ===\n{\n  \"类目名称\": \"Hair Clips & Hair Pins\",\n  \"月销量\": 78385,\n  \"月销量环比\": -13.98,\n  \"平均价格\": \"$4.24\",\n  \"中位数价格\": \"$2.52\",\n  \"平均评价数\": 665,\n  \"平均星级\": 4.69,\n  \"Top300产品来源店铺数\": 156,\n  \"Top10产品月销量占比\": 35.13,\n  \"Top10卖家月销量占比\": 44.91,\n  \"上线3个月内新品数量\": 44,\n  \"上线3个月内新品月销量和\": 12318,\n  \"上线3个月内新品平均价格\": 3.94,\n  \"上线3个月内新品月销量占比\": 15.71,\n  \"Top50产品\": [\n    {\n      \"标题\": \"Klip Rambut Phalaenopsis, Fesyen Wanita, Gaya Gadis Manis, Rekaan Bunga Phalaenopsis yang Cantik, Sesuai untuk Poni Sisi, Aksesori Rambut\",\n      \"品牌\": \"N/A\",\n      \"周销量\": 603,\n      \"周销量环比\": -45.23,\n      \"月销量\": 4717,\n      \"价格\": \"$0.76\",\n      \"卖家\": \"ALS.Fashion\",\n      \"星级\": 4.7,\n      \"评论数量\": 2798\n    },\n    {\n      \"标题\": \"( BLOOMING BEAUTY ) Fashionable Colorful Flower Hair Clips Grab Hairpin Women Accessories NWD\",\n      \"品牌\": \"N/A\",\n      \"周销量\": 416,\n      \"周销量环比\": -40.06,\n      \"月销量\": 4433,\n      \"价格\": \"$0.62\",\n      \"卖家\": \"NWD\",\n      \"星级\": 4.6,\n      \"评论数量\": 5174\n    },\n    {\n      \"标题\": \"New hair clips for 2026, available in multiple colors, styles, and sizes.UYAA1\",\n      \"品牌\": \"N/A\",\n      \"周销量\": 594,\n      \"周销量环比\": -7.62,\n      \"月销量\": 3268,\n      \"价格\": \"$11.90\",\n      \"卖家\": \"UYAAI.MY\",\n      \"星级\": 4.8,\n      \"评论数量\": 2251\n    },\n    {\n      \"标题\": \"Korean Plush Scrunchies Hairband  Ins Elastic Hair Band Tie Accessories Women Pengikat Rambut Wanita\",\n      \"品牌\": \"N/A\",\n      \"周销量\": 33,\n      \"周销量环比\": -91.79,\n      \"月销量\": 3168,\n      \"价格\": \"$2.