{"type":"message","id":"d15da7ef","parentId":"2a4d21ea","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'm getting somewhere!\n\n**MY站各发饰品类平均价格：**\n- Hair Accessories (905864): **$7.52均价**，中位数$4.70，月销环比+13.07% ✅ 增长中\n- Scrunchies (908424): $6.88均价，中位数$2.39（偏低）\n- Heatless Styling (700789): $12.96均价！但月销环比-40%\n\n**Hair Accessories** is the star - average price $7.52, median $4.70, and it's GROWING at +13%. \n\nNow let me dig into the actual products within Hair Accessories to find the specific high-margin items. I should also check VN and ID sites for similar premium categories, and look at PH and GB to see if they have better pricing. With my remaining quota, I can afford to be more aggressive and test different product types directly to identify which ones have the best margin potential.\n","thinkingSignature":"fb4803d47d1fe72b3891ec3f2d8427b9ae32d1188387062ec1ce658b2cba983d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**MY Hair Accessories 类目：均价$7.52，月销增长+13%！**\n\n这是我们要的高价增长品类！现在让我批量扫描所有站点的高价类目：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4dddd612e54a44fd857328c1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"========== 越南 VN 类目扫描 ==========\" && \\\nfor node in 908552 605271 908424; do\n  result=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=$node site=VN --output json 2>&1)\n  avg=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('平均价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  mid=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('中位数价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  growth=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('月销量环比','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  name=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('类目名称','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  echo \"node=$node $name | 均价:$avg 中位:$mid 增长:$growth%\"\ndone\n\necho \"\" && echo \"========== 马来西亚 MY 类目扫描 ==========\" && \\\nfor node in 908552 605271 908424 905864 700789; do\n  result=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=$node site=MY --output json 2>&1)\n  avg=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('平均价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  mid=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('中位数价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  growth=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('月销量环比','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  name=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('类目名称','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  echo \"node=$node $name | 均价:$avg 中位:$mid 增长:$growth%\"\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4823,"output":776,"cacheRead":79801,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85400,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646602603,"responseId":"0671b5cbef7637d91e9a76ec30dbb98a"}}
