{"type":"message","id":"e3157977","parentId":"52e19924","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d3da1b98d96e42df874827be","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 601 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if neede"}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"rapid-glade","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"========== 越南 VN 类目扫描 ==========\nnode=908552 Hair Clips & Hair Pins | 均价:$27758.15 中位:$20000.00 增长:-1.85%\nnode=605271 Headbands | 均价:$36428.76 中位:$23000.00 增长:59.98%\nnode=908424 Hairbands & Scrunchies | 均价:$33416.07 中位:$4000.00 增长:-7.01%\n\n========== 马来西亚 MY 类目扫描 ==========\nnode=908552 Hair Clips & Hair Pins | 均价:$4.24 中位:$2.52 增长:-13.98%\nnode=605271 Headbands | 均价:$7.52 中位:$4.70 增长:13.07%\nnode=908424 Hairbands & Scrunchies | 均价:$6.88 中位:$2.39 增长:-13.73%\nnode=905864 Headbands | 均价:$7.52 中位:$4.70 增长:13.07%\nnode=700789 Hair Styling Tools | 均价:$12.96 中位:$3.89 增长:-40.13%\n","name":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780646640260}}
{"type":"message","id":"435b815d","parentId":"e3157977","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the MY prices seem off - the VN prices are in VND (27758.15 is 27,758 VND = ~$1.11), while MY prices are in USD ($4.24). That makes sense - the API returns prices in local currency.\n\nNow let me compile the comparison:\n\n**越南 VN (价格单位：VND 盾)**\n- Hair Clips (908552): 均价27,758₫($1.11) 中位20,000₫($0.80) 增长-1.85% ❌\n- Headbands (605271): 均价36,428₫($1.46) 中位23,000₫($0.92) 增长+59.98% ✅\n\n\n- Scrunchies (908424): 均价33,416₫($1.34) 中位4,000₫($0.16) 增长-7.01% ❌\n\n**马来西亚 MY (价格单位：USD)**\n- Hair Clips (908552): 均价$4.24 中位$2.52 增长-13.98% ⚠️\n- Headbands (605271): 均价$7.52 中位$4.70 增长+13.07% ✅\n- Scrunchies (908424): 均价$6.88 中位$2.39 增长-13.73% ❌\n- Hair Accessories (905864): 均价$7.52 中位$4.70 增长+13.07% ✅\n- Hair Styling Tools (700789): 均价$12.96 中位$3.89 增长-40.13% ⚠️ 价格高但下滑\n\nMY站的价格明显更高，Headbands和Hair Accessories的7美元以上均价加上两位数增长最有潜力。Styling Tools虽然单价最高但下滑厉害，Hair Clips虽然价格不错却在萎缩。\n\n现在需要深入这些增长品类，看看Top产品里有哪些具体的高价商品能满足毛利率70%的要求。\n\n我已经识别出MY Hair Accessories (nodeId=905864)这个增长品类，接下来应该扫描MY、ID、PH等站点的发饰品类，对比泰国站点找出最优价格带，然后提取这些品类的Top产品进行详细分析。\n","thinkingSignature":"7609c6f4d1a952043648339530ed8800a4d950eaefdd48c62197954393e539c6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n太好了！价格带对比出来了：\n\n| 站点 | 类目 | 均价 | 中位数 | 增长 |\n|------|------|------|--------|------|\n| **MY** | Hair Accessories | **$7.52** | $4.70 | **+13%** ✅ |\n| **MY** | Headbands | **$7.52** | $4.70 | **+13%** ✅ |\n| **MY** | Scrunchies | $6.88 | $2.39 | -14% |\n| VN | Headbands | 36,428₫($1.46) | $0.92 | **+60%** ✅ |\n| VN | Hair Clips | 27,758₫($1.11) | $0.80 | -2% |\n\n**结论：MY 站(马来)价格是 VN 的 5 倍！** 现在让我扫 MY 和 ID 的更多类目，然后直接抓高价产品：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46a807e1166e4eaab3ae94ae","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"========== ID 印尼 类目扫描 ==========\" && \\\nfor kw in \"hair clip\" \"headband\" \"scrunchie\" \"hair accessory\"; do\n  nodes=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"$kw\" site=ID --output json 2>&1)\n  echo \"关键词[$kw]: $nodes\"\ndone\n\necho \"\" && echo \"========== PH 菲律宾 类目扫描 ==========\" && \\\nfor kw in \"hair clip\" \"headband\" \"scrunchie\" \"hair accessory\"; do\n  nodes=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"$kw\" site=PH --output json 2>&1)\n  echo \"关键词[$kw]: $nodes\"\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4711,"output":876,"cacheRead":81086,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780646640289,"responseId":"0671b5f1d9e5a82fe8dc7b797259bb90"}}
