{"type":"message","id":"bc3fd702","parentId":"62145ee5","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:14:55.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It worked! Feishu auto-created the \"马来西亚\" option in the SingleSelect field when I wrote a record with that value. So now the站点 field should have \"马来西亚\" as an option.\n\nNow let me:\n1. Delete the test record\n2. Confirm the站点 field now has马来西亚\n3. Update the SOP to include MY站\n4. Start a proper scan for MY站点高价产品\n","thinkingSignature":"4d995d44edc9a30e05c1add5b5917cc91cb07024cc9c36c8472cb84d5b5a740f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n太好了！飞书自动创建了\"马来西亚\"选项！\n\n**站点字段已自动加入\"马来西亚\"。** 现在删掉测试记录，然后我们正式开工扫描MY站：\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 完成：多维表站点字段已更新\n\n现在有：**越南/VN、泰国、马来西亚** 三个站点选项。\n\n---\n\n### 📊 Sorftime 数据扫描结果（关键发现）\n\n| 站点 | 类目 | 均价 | 中位数 | 月增长 |\n|------|------|------|--------|--------|\n| **MY** | Hair Accessories | **$7.52** | $4.70 | **+13%** ✅ |\n| **MY** | Headbands | **$7.52** | $4.70 | **+13%** ✅ |\n| **MY** | Hair Clips | $4.24 | $2.52 | -14% |\n| VN | Headbands | $1.46 | $0.92 | **+60%** ✅ |\n| PH | Hair Accessories | $57 PHP≈$1 | - | **+30%** ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### 🏆 现在开始正式扫 MY 马来西亚高价黑马！\n\n额度充足（29,845次），让我现在大规模扫描MY站所有发饰品类，找高价+高增长的产品：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6396e2e059c4f42b5b5874a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"========== MY 马来西亚 全部发饰品类深度扫描 ==========\" && \\\n\n# 先搜所有相关类目节点\necho \"\" && echo \"=== 类目节点发现 ===\" && \\\nfor kw in \"hair clip\" \"hair claw\" \"headband\" \"scrunchie\" \"hair accessory\" \"hair pin\" \"hair band\" \"bobby pin\" \"hair tie\"; do\n  result=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_name_search searchName=\"$kw\" site=MY --output json 2>&1)\n  nodes=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; data=json.load(sys.stdin); [print(f'{x[\\\"类目名称\\\"]}|{x[\\\"nodeid\\\"]}') for x in data]\" 2>/dev/null)\n  if [ -n \"$nodes\" ]; then\n    echo \"[$kw]: $nodes\"\n  fi\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provide