{"type":"message","id":"860b0b04","parentId":"16e0c00b","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:34:12.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to focus on Vietnam (VN) first. They're saying \"先搞定VN\" which means \"let's first get Vietnam sorted out.\"\n\nThe issue is that:\n1. VN TikTok data doesn't return product links\n2. VN prices are very low ($0.80-$1.60)\n\nBut the user wants to focus on VN first, so let me:\n1. Acknowledge the VN priority\n2. Find a way to get product links for VN data\n3. Understand the VN pricing issue and what to do about it\n\nFor product links - the category_report doesn't return links. But maybe there's another tool or approach. Let me check if there's a way to construct TikTok shop URLs from the product title/seller info.\n\n\nI'm realizing I can't extract product links from the category_report endpoint, so I need to explore whether there's a separate API call that can retrieve product URLs for VN listings.","thinkingSignature":"35cfeca11e4ebf290309dea03115e1822e5af7151b7cea3086792d6912c3f9a3"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先搞定 VN。\n\n链接的问题我来解决——`category_report` 不返回链接，但我可以换个方式：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c2be64gt644v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"=== 测试 tiktok_similar_product 能否返回链接 ===\" && \\\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product searchName=\"hair clip vietnam\" page=1 site=VN --output json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nif isinstance(data, list) and len(data) > 0:\n    print('字段列表:', list(data[0].keys()))\n    print('示例:', json.dumps(data[0], ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)[:800])\nelif isinstance(data, dict):\n    print('字段列表:', list(data.keys()))\n    print('内容:', json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)[:800])\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"调用失败或无数据\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":412,"cacheRead":94986,"