{"type":"message","id":"299ba7ac","parentId":"860b0b04","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:34:19.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c2be64gt644v_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 测试 tiktok_similar_product 能否返回链接 ===\n字段列表: ['ProductId', '主图', 'Title', '品牌', '周销量', '月销量', '价格', '卖家', '星级', '评论数量']\n示例: {\n  \"ProductId\": \"1734141996809291509\",\n  \"主图\": \"https://p16-oec-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-aphluv4xwc-sg/8570dfe0be20488cbe4241cff5091ef9~tplv-aphluv4xwc-crop-webp:1200:1200.webp?dr=15592&t=555f072d&ps=933b5bde&shp=8dbd94bf&shcp=607f11de&idc=my&from=2378011839\",\n  \"Title\": \"Kẹp Tết Tóc Mái 3 Tầng - Phủ Lớp Nhung Nên Vận Chuyển Sẽ Trầy Nhẹ\",\n  \"品牌\": \"Generic\",\n  \"周销量\": 7378,\n  \"月销量\": 50666,\n  \"价格\": 16999,\n  \"卖家\": \"M.A.I COSMETICS\",\n  \"星级\": 4.6,\n  \"评论数量\": 14338\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7111,"aggregated":"=== 测试 tiktok_similar_product 能否返回链接 ===\n字段列表: ['ProductId', '主图', 'Title', '品牌', '周销量', '月销量', '价格', '卖家', '星级', '评论数量']\n示例: {\n  \"ProductId\": \"1734141996809291509\",\n  \"主图\": \"https://p16-oec-sg.ibyteimg.com/tos-alisg-i-aphluv4xwc-sg/8570dfe0be20488cbe4241cff5091ef9~tplv-aphluv4xwc-crop-webp:1200:1200.webp?dr=15592&t=555f072d&ps=933b5bde&shp=8dbd94bf&shcp=607f11de&idc=my&from=2378011839\",\n  \"Title\": \"Kẹp Tết Tóc Mái 3 Tầng - Phủ Lớp Nhung Nên Vận Chuyển Sẽ Trầy Nhẹ\",\n  \"品牌\": \"Generic\",\n  \"周销量\": 7378,\n  \"月销量\": 50666,\n  \"价格\": 16999,\n  \"卖家\": \"M.A.I COSMETICS\",\n  \"星级\": 4.6,\n  \"评论数量\": 14338\n}","cwd":"/home/halei/workspace-tts"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780648459944}}
{"type":"message","id":"14d00727","parentId":"299ba7ac","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:34:36.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`tiktok_similar_product` has `ProductId` but no direct link. However, I can construct a TikTok shop URL from the ProductId. TikTok shop product URLs typically look like:\n- https://shop.tiktok.com/product/productId\n- Or we can search for the product by ID\n\nBut actually, the better approach is to use the `ProductId` field which is the TikTok product ID, and construct the URL from it. TikTok shop links usually follow this format:\n- https://shop.tiktok.com/view/product/<PRODUCT_ID>\n- Or: https://tp.ink/product/<PRODUCT_ID>\n\n\nI can build a direct link using the format `https://shop.tiktok.com/view/product/<PRODUCT_ID>?region=VN&language=vi`, though the exact domain might vary. Alternatively, I could just show the ProductId and let the user search for it manually. Now let me focus on pulling the actual VN data—I need to scan the Hair Clips category for Vietnam since that's what the user prioritized, and I've already identified the relevant nodeId.\n\nThe real problem I'm seeing is that VN prices are too low (10,000-40,000 VND) for the毛利率≥70% strategy to work, but I should present the data clearly and let the user decide if they want to pivot to higher-priced items like the ones selling for 80,000+ VND.","thinkingSignature":"60e40007a44c2e6ffe393e8bb1ee7283f190f5f0f1be96c8f9e90eb6431db69c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n`tiktok_similar_product` 返回的是 `ProductId`（TikTok产品ID），我可以构造链接。同时我发现越南站也有高价品！\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 先扫描VN所有发饰品类，找高价正增长黑马\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eyku0sue5g06_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"=== VN 越南 全部发饰品类价格扫描 ===\" && \\\nfor node in 908552 605271 908424 905864 700789 601344; do\n  result=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=$node site=VN --output json 2>&1)\n  avg=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('平均价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  mid=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('中位数价格','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  growth=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('月销量环比','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  name=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('类目名称','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  total=$(echo \"$result\" | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(d.get('月销量','ERR'))\" 2>/dev/null)\n  echo \"[$node] $name | 均价:$avg | 中位:$mid | 增长:$growth% | 月销:$total\"\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43816,"output":679,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780648460024,"responseId":"0671bd0c10c6a4010c55173419d0b325"}}
