{"type":"message","id":"1043ced7","parentId":"f90d2600","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:35:18.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of VN categories:\n\n| Node | 类目 | 均价(VND) | 中位(VND) | 月增长 | 月销 |\n|------|------|-----------|-----------|--------|------|\n| 605271/905864 | Headbands | 36,428 VND ($1.46) | 23,000 VND ($0.92) | **+59.98%** ✅ | 145,577 |\n| 908552 | Hair Clips | 27,758 VND ($1.11) | 20,000 VND ($0.80) | -1.85% | 449,516 |\n\n\n| 908424 | Hairbands & Scrunchies | 33,416 VND ($1.34) | 4,000 VND ($0.16) | -7.01% | 268,026 |\n| 700789 | Hair Styling Tools | 46,100 VND ($1.84) | 35,000 VND ($1.40) | -27.65% | 138,566 |\n| 601344 | Hijab Pins | 50,253 VND ($2.01) | 55,000 VND ($2.20) | -82.03% | 69 |\n\nThe standout performers are clearly the headbands at 36,428 VND with nearly 60% monthly growth and the hair clips with massive volume at 449K monthly sales, though both categories show declining trends except for that headband spike. The hijab pins are essentially dead with almost no volume and a steep decline.\n\nNow I need to dig into the headband data more carefully since it showed such strong growth, and I should also scan for products priced above 80,000 VND to see what's driving the higher-end market.","thinkingSignature":"65d7c372ce4c89147055cfa3ddded50385f03d19c1648ac2e072d905bc5b10c5"},{"type":"text","text":"**VN 越南价格分析：**\n\n| 类目 | 均价 | 中位数 | 月增长 | 月销 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|------|\n| Headbands | 36,428₫ | 23,000₫ | **+60%** ✅ | 145,577 |\n| Hair Clips | 27,758₫ | 20,000₫ | -2% | 449,516 |\n| Hairbands | 33,416₫ | 4,000₫ | -7% | 268,026 |\n| Hair Styling | 46,100₫ | 35,000₫ | -28% | 138,566 |\n\n**重点：VN Headbands 月增长+60%，均价36,428₫（$1.46）** 虽然价格还是低，但增长率很漂亮！\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 抓 VN Headbands 高价黑马 + 链接\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1utkwx5685f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\nmcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=605271 site=VN --output json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json, re\n\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint(f'类目: {d[\\\"类目名称\\\"]} | 均价: {d[\\\"平均价格\\\"]} | 中位数: {d[\\\"中位数价格\\\"]} | 月增长: {d[\\\"月销量环比\\\"]}%')\nprint('='*90)\n\ntop50 = d.get('Top50产品', [])\n\n# 按价格降序 + 正增长优先\ndef get_price(p):\n    try: \n        price_str = str(p.get('价格','0')).replace('₫','').replace('$','').replace(',','').strip()\n        return float(price_str)\n    except: return 0\n\n# 先看高价品TOP15\nprint('=== 高价品 TOP15 (价格降序) ===')\nsorted_price = sorted(top50, key=get_price, reverse=True)\nfor i, p in enumerate(sorted_price[:15], 1):\n    price = p.get('价格','N/A')\n    title = p.get('标题','N/A')[:55]\n    sales = p.get('月销量', 0)\n    stars = p.get('星级','N/A')\n    growth = p.get('周销量环比', 0)\n    print(f'{i:2d}. {price:>12s} | 月销{sales:>6d} | ⭐{stars} | 增长{growth:>8.1f}% | {title}')\n\nprint('')\n# 正增长高价品\npositive = [p for p in top50 if p.get('周销量环比', 0) > 0]\nsorted_pos = sorted(positive, key=lambda p: (get_price(p), p.get('周销量环比',0)), reverse=True)\nprint(f'=== 正增长产品 ({len(positive)}个) ===')\nfor i, p in enumerate(sorted_pos[:10], 1):\n    price = p.get('价格','N/A')\n    title = p.get('标题','N/A')[:55]\n    sales = p.get('月销量', 0)\n    stars = p.get('星级','N/A')\n    growth = p.get('周销量环比', 0)\n    print(f'{i:2d}. {price:>12s} | 月销{sales:>6d} | ⭐{stars} | 增长+{growth:>6.1f}% | {title}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44875,"output":1159,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780648496198,"responseId":"0671bd3044b8a5f4cf8c3720301b4277"}}
