{"type":"message","id":"9d463a28","parentId":"a8b726af","timestamp":"2026-06-05T08:36:34.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only 2 products meet the criteria (≥30,000₫ and positive growth). Let me check 1688 prices for these 2 products and calculate margins:1. PASIER gift box headband at 109,000₫ ($4.36)2. Princess velvet headband at 39,000₫ ($1.56)For the 39,000₫ product:\n- Price: 39,000 VND = $1.56 USD\n- Platform fee (30%): $0.47\n- Logistics (15%): $0.23\n- Remaining for 1688 cost: $1.56 - $0.47 - $0.23 = $0.86\n\n\n- 1688 price needed: $0.86 / 7.2 = ¥6.2 → quite high, might be possible\n\nFor the 109,000₫ product, I need to work backwards from the margin requirement. If I want 70% gross margin on the selling price, I can allocate the remaining 30% across platform fees, logistics, and the 1688 cost, which means the 1688 price needs to be ¥5.7. Let me search for these products on 1688 to verify the actual prices.\n\nI'm also reconsidering whether to expand my search criteria—I could lower the price threshold to include items ≥20,000₫ while maintaining the positive growth and margin requirements, or I could target the 20,000-30,000₫ range specifically for velvet and ribbon products since they tend to have better margins. The 109,000₫ category at 154% growth is clearly attractive despite the higher price point.","thinkingSignature":"dc30a87d9a4fa949b9741c6a386fbf1deb5f5c71577e26bfe66b1eb51a5e243c"},{"type":"text","text":"VN Headbands 符合条件的不多（高价+正增长很难同时满足）。让我放宽一点，抓 **20,000-30,000₫ 正增长品**，同时查 1688 验证毛利：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dfa0zqn71fio_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && \\\n\necho \"=== VN Headbands 扫描（≥15,000₫ 正增长品）===\" && \\\n\nresult=$(mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report nodeId=605271 site=VN --output json 2>&1)\n\necho \"$result\" | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json, re\n\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\ntop50 = d.get('Top50产品', [])\n\ndef get_price(p):\n    try: \n        price_str = str(p.get('价格','0')).replace('₫','').replace('$','').replace(',','').strip()\n        return float(price_str)\n    except: return 0\n\n# 放宽条件：价格≥15000 且 正增长\nfiltered = [p for p in top50 if get_price(p) >= 15000 and p.get('周销量环比', 0) > 0]\nsorted_prods = sorted(filtered, key=lambda p: (get_price(p), p.get('周销量环比',0)), reverse=True)\n\nprint(f'符合条件: {len(sorted_prods)}个 (≥15,000₫ 且正增长)')\nprint()\nfor i, p in enumerate(sorted_prods[:10], 1):\n    price = get_price(p)\n    price_usd = price / 25000  # approx VND to USD\n    price_display = p.get('价格','N/A')\n    title = p.get('标题','N/A')[:60]\n    sales = p.get('月销量', 0)\n    stars = p.get('星级','N/A')\n    growth = p.get('周销量环比', 0)\n    print(f'{i}. {price_display:>12s} (\\${price_usd:.2f}) | 月销{sales:>5d} | ⭐{stars} | 增长+{growth:.1f}%')\n    print(f'   {title}')\n    print()\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49449,"output":836,"cacheRead":54174,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780648576134,"responseId":"0671bd8097d8a60c159b3b04f406524f"}}
